      <p id="Par35">Finally, we assume that all <italic>L</italic> individuals are independent, then the overall joint distribution for all cells across all individuals becomes<disp-formula id="Equ5"><label>5</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M71">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
