    <sec id="Sec13">
      <title>Classification and computational acceleration</title>
      <p id="Par39">To further improve the computational efficiency, we provide a supervised option in BAMM-SC. Specifically, for very large-scale dataset, we use BAMM-SC to train a prediction model using a subset of cells from each individual and predict the clustering labels for the rest of cells. First, we randomly select a subset of cells from each individual and applied BAMM-SC on these selected cells. The estimate of <inline-formula id="IEq48"><alternatives><tex-math id="M111">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
